docstr: `RAN` — Real pseudo-random number ### Description For compatibility with HP FORTRAN 77/iX, the `RAN` intrinsic is provided as an alias for `RAND`. See RAND for complete documentation. ### Standard GNU extension ### Class Function ### See also RAND, RANDOM_NUMBER
